<p><b>How to heal from heartbreak in 30 days?</b> Try a feel-good activity Set aside time every day for doing something that feels positive, whether that's journaling, meeting up with a close friend, or watching a show that makes you laugh. Scheduling in moments that bring you joy is vital for healing a broken heart.</p>
